column1: # Readings for the following periods are apportioned:
# The following readings are estimates and have been omitted:
# The reading for February 1941 is estimated for snow and has been retained.
# The readings for January-March 1942 are part-estimated for snow and have been retained.
# The readings for February-March 1947 are estimated for snow and have been retained.
# The reading for January 1950 is part estimated and has been retained.
# The 1950s sheet gives the location as Cockayne Lodge, which seems to be Bransdale Lodge on the map.
# The original grid reference on the 1950s sheet has been used, as this is a better match for the elevation and church directions provided.
